            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hm? What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I was just thinking about how you seem to believe Oskar. About how he says he can hear the voices of plants."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x11b,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "He's my own boy. I would know in an instant if he was lying or not."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x11b,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I can't hear them myself, but if he says he can hear them, then I'm sure they're talking."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x11b,
            "name_id": 0x10,
            "extra_id": 0xe,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Also, for all these years, anything he says that's related to plants has never been wrong."
